#       Configuration file for Circularly polarized Alfven wave MHD problem
#	James Stone, www.astro.princeton.edu/~jstone

REQUIRES physics/Hydro/HydroMain 
REQUIRES physics/Eos/EosMain/Gamma

D   tiny	    Threshold value used for numerical zero
D   rx	            advection angle = atan(rx/ry)
D   ry
D   U0 		    Strength of initial vector fields
D   B0              Magnitude of circularly polarized Alfven wave
D   P0              Initial pressure
D   steady          Dynamics of the problem

PARAMETER tiny         REAL     1.e-16
PARAMETER rx	       REAL     1.
PARAMETER ry           REAL     2.
PARAMETER U0	       REAL     1.0
PARAMETER B0           REAL     0.1
PARAMETER P0	       REAL     0.1
PARAMETER steady       BOOLEAN  FALSE
VARIABLE BTRA
VARIABLE XNOR
